{"article_id":"Anlh6LZJVWrEVJ7X","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump on Monday called the criminal case against former national security adviser Michael Flynn \" very unfair , \"","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"claiming","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"he and Hillary Clinton both \" lied \" to the FBI","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"but only Flynn faced consequences .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"The president ' s comments ,","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"made to reporters","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"as he left Washington for a policy announcement in Utah ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"saw Trump wading deeper into the Flynn investigation","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"even after a weekend tweet landed the White House in hot water .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"On Monday , Trump said","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"he feels \" badly \" for Flynn ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"who pleaded guilty on Friday to giving false statements to the FBI about his Russia contacts .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"\" Hillary Clinton lied many times to the FBI ,","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"nothing happened to her .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"Flynn lied","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"and they destroyed his life , \"","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"Trump said .","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"The president ,","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"without offering specifics ,","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"his 2016 Democratic rival \" lied many times \" during her FBI interview in early July .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"\" Nothing happened to her .","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"Flynn lied","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"and it ' s like they ruined his life .","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"Very unfair , \"","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"Trump said ,","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"echoing a weekend tweet","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"in which he asked","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"whether a \" double standard \" was at play .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"Clinton was interviewed by FBI agents as part of the investigation into her exclusive use of a private email system while secretary of state .","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"After that interview , then-FBI Director James Comey called her actions extremely careless","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"without recommending criminal charges .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"Trump also noted over the weekend","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"that Clinton was not recorded or under oath during that interview .","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"On Sunday , Sen. Lindsey Graham , R-S.C. , suggested","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"Trump might want to think twice","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"before tweeting and commenting on the Russia case .","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"\" You tweet and comment regarding ongoing criminal investigations at your own peril , \"","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"he said on CBS ' \" Face the Nation . \"","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"This was after Trump ' s account tweeted Saturday :","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"\" I had to fire General Flynn","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"because he lied to the Vice President and the FBI .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"He has pled guilty to those lies .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"It is a shame","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"because his actions during the transition were lawful .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"There was nothing to hide ! \"","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"That tweet immediately caused problems for the White House ,","depth":5},{"id":47,"text":"as some legal experts said","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"it potentially exposed the president to obstruction of justice allegations","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"- since ,","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"according to the tweet ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"he would have known","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"Flynn lied to agents","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"when he allegedly asked Comey to lay off the Flynn investigation","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"and later fired Comey .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Trump said earlier this year","depth":4},{"id":56,"text":"that he fired Flynn","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"only for lying to Vice President Pence about the issue .","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"Trump ' s personal lawyer John Dowd later said","depth":4},{"id":59,"text":"he was the one","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"who wrote that tweet ,","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"he \" did not mean to break news . \"","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"Dowd attempted to explain Sunday","depth":5},{"id":64,"text":"that the tweet was referring to then-acting Attorney General Sally Yates telling White House Counsel Don McGahn in January","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"that Flynn had \" given the agents the same story","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"he gave the vice president . \"","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"He also said","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"the agents seemed to think","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"Flynn was confused .","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"\" All","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"the president knew","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"was that the department was not accusing him of lying , \"","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"Dowd said .","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"Trump over the weekend denied","depth":4},{"id":75,"text":"that he asked Comey to stop investigating Flynn .","depth":4},{"id":76,"text":"Sen. Dianne Feinstein , D-Calif. , the top Democrat on the Senate Judiciary Committee , said on NBC ' s \" Meet the Press \" on Sunday","depth":5},{"id":77,"text":"that the panel has begun to see `` the putting together of a case of obstruction of justice '' against Trump .","depth":5},{"id":78,"text":"Flynn is now cooperating with Special Counsel Robert Mueller ' s investigators in the Russia meddling case ,","depth":5},{"id":79,"text":"though it ' s unclear what exactly he might reveal about Trump and his associates .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":159,"left":137,"right":158,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":113,"right":136,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"pare